tion |\n\n#### 2.5 Scheme Directory — ❌ MISSING\n\n- Spec expects `clientset/versioned/scheme/` — **does not exist**\n- Scheme registration appears to be in `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/` instead\n\n### 3. Build Status — ❌ FAIL\n\n```\ncmd/router/main.go:58:67: server.GetRouter undefined (type *router.Server has no field or method GetRouter)\n```\n\n`cmd/router/main.go:58` calls `server.GetRouter()` but `*router.Server` has no such method. The `Router` interface exists separately in `pkg/router/router.go:8` but is not exposed via `Server`.\n\n### 4. Test Status — ⚠️ NO TESTS\n\nNo test files exist in any `client-go/` package. `go test ./client-go/...` reports `[no test files]` for all 6 packages.\n\n---\n\n## Summary\n\n| Area | Verdict |\n|------|---------|\n| 4 CLI binaries | ✅ PASS |\n| Clientset Interface | ⚠️ PARTIAL — missing `Discovery()`, 3 of 4 constructors, no `discovery.DiscoveryClient` embedding |\n| RuntimeV1alpha1Interface | ⚠️ PARTIAL — missing `RESTClient()`, uses ObjectStore instead of REST |\n| AgentRuntimeInterface | ⚠️ PARTIAL — missing `DeleteCollection`, `AgentRuntimeExpansion`, `Watch`/`Patch` are stubs |\n| CodeInterpreterInterface | ⚠️ PARTIAL — same gaps as AgentRuntime |\n| File structure | ⚠️ Deviates from spec (no `versioned/`, no separate files, no `scheme/`) |\n| Build | ❌ FAIL — `router.GetRouter()` undefined |\n| Tests | ❌ NO TESTS |","time":{"start":1775849391130,"end":1775849391130}}}
